name: CinemaQuotes-OfficeSpaceEdition
0:
”Alexa, open Cinema Quotes”
”Read a Milton quote”
”Read a quote from The Bobs”
skdetail:
Rated: Mature. This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: cinema quotes
des: Hear all the quotes from the cult movie Office Space. Listen to Milton ("I believe you have my stapler"), Peter, Samir, Michael Bolton, Lumbergh, The Bobs and the entire gang. Just say 'Open the Cinema'. When prompted, ask for a quote from one of the characters. After the first quote, say YES for a random quote from one of the characters or ask for another quote from a specific character. Enjoy a good case of the Mondays!
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
